<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Excerpted from <span class="c-mrkdwn__highlight">the</span> book</em> <a href="https://bookshop.org/a/132/9780063454385" class="external" target="_blank">On Natural Capital: The Value of the World Around Us</a><span class="c-mrkdwn__highlight"> <em>by Partha Dasgupta. P</em></span><em>rovided courtesy <span class="c-mrkdwn__highlight">of</span> <span class="c-mrkdwn__highlight">Mariner</span> Books, an imprint <span class="c-mrkdwn__highlight">of</span> HarperCollins Publishers. Copyright © 2026. Reprinted by permission.</em></p><div class="insert-post-ads" style="clear:both;width:100%;margin:0 0 20px 0;"><span>Article continues after advertisement</span><!-- GAM 22020028882/LTHB_lithubcom/Article_Incontent_4 -->
<div data-fuse="Article_Incontent_4"></div></div>
</p>							</div>
